  <brief_title>INR Comparison Testing in Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of INR Determined by Point-of-Care to Standard Laboratory Testing Before and After Reversal of Heparin in Cardiac Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
